These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, reggae, ambient
1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
3. the fan of funk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | reggae | funk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | february | july | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, corn, kale
1. the person eating corn is in an even position##4
2. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Food   | cranberry | corn | kale |

 #################################

 
