.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, iced-tea
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea | hot-chocolate |

 